Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请大家见证真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是场精彩的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
